txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Jewelled sword sheaths from the intelligent creatures near Gath Forthnír. Deilvery of the items should be made to Areneth at the hidden Ranger-outpost.
'Get the sword sheaths from our enemies so that we may better protect the few weapons that we have.'
Council of the North Task: Jewelled Sword Sheaths
The Rangers at Gath Forthnír await a delivery of jewelled sword sheaths to be made to Areneth.
Deliver the jewelled sword sheaths to Areneth at Gath Forthnír in Angmar
You have accepted a task to collect and deliver jewelled sword sheaths from the intelligent creatures near Gath Forthnír to Areneth at the hidden Ranger-camp.
Wanted: Jewelled sword sheaths from the intelligent creatures near Gath Forthnír.
